{"tid":536530,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打們當初係點決定自己嘅將來？","createTime":"2018-01-22T01:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T08:20:01.000Z","uid":147832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f72c03f2fb62451d16645c34d2eaa82519ce6fc1","tid":536530,"uid":147832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T01:01:04.000Z","msg":"小弟係個垃圾asso仔，讀埋嚟緊嗰幾個月就讀晒兩年asso，雖然GPA係唔低，都足以上得返U，但係自問我真係無心向學，每日返學都係渾渾噩噩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我其實對bartender呢行幾有興趣，但係讀緊嘅嘢同酒呢方面完全冇關，完全係白紙一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想問問各位巴打當初係點決定自己將來要行咩路，應唔應該庸庸碌碌咁讀多兩年求其搵份工就算，定應該放棄讀書，去搵方法做bartender？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8475c420282b544efd5521131d8397336480e93","tid":536530,"uid":79686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"諗下十年後既自己會唔會後悔而家既決定"},{"pid":"657c4abbf6c41e1d8518f8b9889a06175077dfa6","tid":536530,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"有錢咪讀到大學畢業，間中兼職酒吧囉<br />\n（不負責鳩up"},{"pid":"96256225b6ef5cda9667a0d7062561a031cf2d54","tid":536530,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"existence precedes essence"},{"pid":"511daecb0cb292e4ef84aa62de3a56ad5d8cd220","tid":536530,"uid":81380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"點解你講到讀多2年書就做唔到 bartender？"},{"pid":"1623a00dfe39f4251eef41d2e0437382d137ef2e","tid":536530,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"做bar